# LLM Configuration for Manager Insight Agent (Optional)
# This file is an example. Copy to .env.local and add your real keys.

# ============================================
# OPTION 1: Custom OpenAI-compatible endpoint
# ============================================
# LLM_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# LLM_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# LLM_PROVIDER_NAME=openai

# ============================================
# OPTION 2: Named providers (auto-configured)
# ============================================
# OpenAI
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# DeepSeek (recommended - cheap and fast)
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Grok (via NewAPI relay or official)
# LLM_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.x.ai/v1
# LLM_MODEL=grok-4.3-fast
# LLM_PROVIDER_NAME=grok

# ============================================
# OPTION 3: Azure OpenAI
# ============================================
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-key
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com
# AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=your-deployment-name
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-10-21

# ============================================
# No keys? No problem!
# ============================================
# Without any keys, the system runs entirely on:
# - Deterministic readiness scoring engine
# - Rule-based study plan generation
# - Local fallback for Manager Insights (no LLM)
# The app works perfectly for demos without any API costs.
